<C>__{sid}
<D>__{three whips. to go.}
<C>__{breeze}
<D>__{when you get a chance.}
<A>__{sid and breeze walk over to theo's booth and slide in. sid's middle fingers are taped to an aluminum splinterior the blender kicks into action. buzz watches the group from the bathroom hall and tries to catch the conversation.}
