<D>__{no, we ain't brothers.}
<C>__{sid}
<D>__{you know why we call him breeze?}
<A>__{sid puts a hand near breezes left ear and blows into breeze's right ear. he makes fluttering motions with his hand as if wind was hitting it. breeze's face breaks into a smile as he pushes sid away.}
